The paper discusses the challenges and opportunities in designing large-scale data processing systems for emerging Big Data analytics and machine learning applications. This topic is closely related to several sub-categories of computer science, including Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Databases (cs.DB), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Software Engineering (cs.SE), and Architecture (cs.AR). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
